WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.950
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:04.950
for joining me again tonight. I

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.630
appreciate everyone coming out

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:09.669
and praying with me. I'm going

00:00:09.679 --> 00:00:11.430
to go over some of the things the Lord's

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:12.950
been talking to me about and what

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:14.629
my wife and I have been studying

00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:19.750
since Friday. I

00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:19.760
am

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:22.390
really

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.470
looking inward and

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:27.429
examining myself and

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:29.990
making sure my thermostat's right. I

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.030
do it all the time. But I was in

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:37.190
prayer, and I felt a

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:38.869
wall,

00:00:38.879 --> 00:00:40.630
and I said, "Lord, what's going on with

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:42.950
me? Can you help me out with some

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:45.190
things? I want to go from

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.670
glory to glory, and I want

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:50.549
to be a good leader for you, and I want

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:53.430
to

00:00:56.640 --> 00:01:01.110
be more effective at the things

00:01:01.110 --> 00:01:01.120
you have

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:02.709
called me

00:01:02.709 --> 00:01:02.719
to do.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:05.270
I don't know how in the natural to do

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:07.429
it without the Holy

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:11.350
Spirit. I need

00:01:11.350 --> 00:01:11.360
you."As

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:13.109
I was praying that morning,

00:01:13.119 --> 00:01:14.789
my wife came in and said,

00:01:14.799 --> 00:01:19.190
"The Lord put

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.590
this book on my heart

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:23.990
by John Bevere.

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.590
We're not finished with the other one

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:28.630
yet, but I feel like we're supposed to

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:31.270
jump off of that one and read

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:33.429
this one because of what I heard this

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:36.550
morning in my spirit. We

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:39.109
haven't read this together yet, but we

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:41.109
have it, and it's

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:42.870
been sitting there. We've read The

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:45.590
Awe of God two or three

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:49.910
times it

00:01:49.910 --> 00:01:49.920
seems."She

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:52.710
brought this book out,

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:55.030
and

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.270
I can honestly tell you, I didn't

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:03.190
know the man could write as well as he

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:07.429
does. It's another

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.430
life-changing book. You may say,

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:11.270
"Brandon, that's an old book. This is

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:14.070
one of his first books he ever

00:02:14.070 --> 00:02:14.080
wrote."How

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:16.470
could you

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.869
have never read that before?

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:21.830
It's The Bait of Satan.

00:02:21.830 --> 00:02:21.840
I

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:24.470
am

00:02:24.470 --> 00:02:24.480
reflecting

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:27.110
on

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:30.070
being offended in these last days.

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:31.830
The scripture in Matthew 24 talks

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:35.589
about how many will

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:37.830
be offended,

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:40.390
and the love of

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:58.949
many shall wax cold. Iniquity

00:02:58.949 --> 00:02:58.959
shall abound.

00:02:58.959 --> 00:03:02.550
In Matthew 24, Jesus

00:03:02.550 --> 00:03:02.560
says,

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:06.630
"And then shall many be offended,

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:10.070
and shall betray one another, and shall

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:12.790
hate one

00:03:12.790 --> 00:03:12.800
another."Jesus

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:16.070
said one of the major signs of

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.949
the end times that we're supposed to

00:03:18.959 --> 00:03:23.509
be looking for is not with the unbeliever,

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:26.550
but with the

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:28.229
believer—people

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:30.949
being offended and walking in

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:32.949
offense.

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:36.229
Many will be offended.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:48.470
That's one of

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:50.149
the major scriptures he uses through

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:53.190
this whole book.

00:03:53.200 --> 00:03:57.750
As I was listening,

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:00.630
I heard him ask the question, "Lord, am

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.869
I offended at so and so?"He didn't

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:04.309
bring up the person's name, but it was

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:07.190
somebody that was dear to him

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:09.910
at one point in time, and the Lord said

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.229
yes.

00:04:12.239 --> 00:04:14.630
I started going over everybody in my

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:16.469
Rolodex

00:04:16.479 --> 00:04:20.469
in my mind, asking if they have offended

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:21.990
me.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:24.629
I didn't realize until I started

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:27.030
going over this book

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:31.030
how many people I had a Rolodex

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:33.430
list of keeping track of what

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.270
they've done wrong and how they offended me

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.030
through ministry, even what I've done in

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:40.550
the last three years,

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:45.990
not releasing it and carrying that.

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:50.310
I saw in the spirit a dam

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:53.909
that looked like a beaver's dam;

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:55.990
it looked like

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:59.749
sticks, metal, and debris

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:01.830
inside.

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:03.430
The Lord showed me this in the

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:05.510
spirit when I was praying, and he said

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:07.909
when you get that offense, that's what

00:05:07.919 --> 00:05:10.469
blocks the

00:05:10.479 --> 00:05:13.590
flow of the anointing and the

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.510
presence on your life. When you hold

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:18.390
offense towards people and

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:20.870
you don't let it go,

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:23.189
it blocks the flow. You have to forgive

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:25.909
them as I have forgiven them. If you don't

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:27.430
forgive them, Brandon, I won't forgive

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:30.790
you.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:34.230
I had all these reasons of why I

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:37.270
felt justified.

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.430
Well, they did this, they said this,

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.670
they ran me down, they talked trash

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.510
about me. I heard it from another

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:45.110
minister that told me they're

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:47.110
saying this and that. You hold all

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:49.990
this hurt in your heart because people

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.990
are mean.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.909
The comment sections are mean and words

00:05:53.919 --> 00:05:55.510
hurt.

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:58.150
Emails hurt.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:00.710
People are just being people, I guess.

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:03.270
But you take offense to some things.

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:05.830
The Lord showed me

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.390
through this book, a healthy spirit

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:11.590
doesn't get offended.

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.590
Diana and I have listened to the sermon

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:15.990
series.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.749
We've listened to it over the last

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:19.909
three days. This is our second time to

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:22.629
listen to it now.

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:25.270
We listened to it all day today. They

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:26.950
had some new stuff that he's bringing

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:28.870
out.

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:30.469
He was teaching some of it

00:06:30.479 --> 00:06:34.870
again.

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.790
The publisher said it was

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:42.550
too much scripture in the book, and they

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:44.390
wouldn't even publish

00:06:44.390 --> 00:06:44.400
it.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:47.270
He gave up on it, was really

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:48.870
down, and there was a lot of things

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:50.790
that he tells through the stories of

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:52.629
what he went through, the persecution

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:54.390
and the offense of trying not to be

00:06:54.400 --> 00:06:55.510
offended right in the book about

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.510
offense.

00:06:57.520 --> 00:06:59.990
I'm going to tell

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:02.070
you,

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:05.830
I would say

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.830
out of me

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.990
telling you all what I feel,

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.469
that every believer—and like I said, I

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:14.790
don't know this

00:07:14.790 --> 00:07:14.800
man—I'm

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:17.189
not trying to sell his books.

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:20.390
I don't push books.

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:22.790
I don't even write books. I don't

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:24.390
try to sell anything to anybody in

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:26.390
the body of Christ. I don't ask for

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:29.350
nothing.

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:31.670
I'm just telling

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.990
you what helps me.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.830
If you say, "Well, Brandon, I

00:07:35.840 --> 00:07:37.990
think that book's

00:07:37.990 --> 00:07:38.000
trash,"that's

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:40.150
your opinion. But I

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:41.510
just wanted to tell you what was

00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:44.870
helping Diana and I. As I started

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:48.790
praying for those that have offended me,

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:55.830
it hurt.

00:07:57.919 --> 00:07:59.589
There's been a lot of people hurt me

00:07:59.599 --> 00:08:03.189
lately, big ministers.

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.670
And I walk away

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:07.589
and you don't realize you've

00:08:07.599 --> 00:08:09.110
stuffed the offense down in there.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:11.189
You're like,

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:12.869
"I don't want

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:15.749
to talk about them right

00:08:15.749 --> 00:08:15.759
now."And

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:18.710
the Lord says,

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:24.070
"You've got to let that go.""Well, I'm not

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:28.230
offended.""Yeah,

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:31.350
you

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:33.509
are."The

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:36.550
more I meditate on the word

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:38.709
and what the Lord told us was coming in

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:41.269
these last days, I don't want to be a

00:08:41.279 --> 00:08:43.990
statistic.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:47.030
Many will be offended. Not me. I'm

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:48.230
going to be healthy

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:50.630
spiritually. He used the example

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:51.990
when he was preaching. He had this big,

00:08:51.990 --> 00:08:52.000
muscular

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.710
guy walk up and just

00:08:54.710 --> 00:08:54.720
shove

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:57.509
him really hard, and it didn't really

00:08:57.519 --> 00:08:59.829
phase him that much. But then he took a

00:08:59.839 --> 00:09:01.670
chair and he said, "If I take this chair

00:09:01.680 --> 00:09:04.949
and break that chair over his

00:09:04.959 --> 00:09:09.910
body, it will wound him.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:12.630
It don't just hurt a little

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:15.430
bit, but that will wound

00:09:15.430 --> 00:09:15.440
him."But

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.949
he started talking about the more

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:19.750
you go to the spiritual gym

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.590
and you work out and you take care of

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.070
yourself spiritually, the more you're

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:25.350
able to take it. He had a

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.509
neighbor that was part of the WWE

00:09:27.519 --> 00:09:29.110
wrestlers,

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:30.949
and they could take chairs and hit him

00:09:30.959 --> 00:09:32.630
upside the head.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:35.430
But because he was so physically fit and

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:38.389
so built like a rock,

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:41.670
those chairs didn't bother him anymore.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:46.150
I started

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:48.870
thinking about that. I've meditated on

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:51.910
that all day long and yesterday. I

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:54.310
just felt like somebody was taking a

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:56.389
piece of sandpaper

00:09:56.399 --> 00:09:58.630
and a

00:09:58.630 --> 00:09:58.640
Brillo

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:00.630
pad and just

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:05.990
rubbing me on the inside

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:08.310
in my soul.

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.710
Same with Diana. She cried, and

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:12.949
she started praying for the

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:14.710
people. We did it as a

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:17.030
family. We took communion over it. I have

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:18.790
practiced it. I'm telling

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:21.190
you, I'm determined to go to the greater

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:23.829
glory.

00:10:23.839 --> 00:10:26.310
I'm determined to walk with him in a

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:28.310
greater measure of the presence of God

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:31.670
on my life than I ever have before.

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:34.230
I know that I have all kinds

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:37.590
of things that I work out;

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:39.829
we all do. We are all a work in

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:42.069
progress, but this is another phase that I

00:10:42.069 --> 00:10:42.079
have

00:10:42.079 --> 00:10:45.590
to really work on.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.829
This is another phase that I realize

00:10:47.839 --> 00:10:50.710
that Brandon is really messed up here

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:55.350
and I have to fix it.

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:58.870
Being jealous of other ministers,

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:00.230
being able to hang out with other

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.990
ministers and they are accepted in other

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.470
crowds and you are not,

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:05.990
and the Lord said, I did not want you in

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.670
that crowd.

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:09.269
Well, I would like to hang out over there

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:12.630
and be friends. No, that is not what I

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:14.630
want for you.

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:16.310
Well, I do not understand why they

00:11:16.310 --> 00:11:16.320
are

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:18.230
accepted.

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:19.990
And then you take offense to not being

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:22.389
accepted. It all goes back to a lot of

00:11:22.399 --> 00:11:24.230
insecurities from going through

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:27.110
school. You are not at the popular

00:11:27.120 --> 00:11:30.389
kid table. You are at the

00:11:30.389 --> 00:11:30.399
bullies,

00:11:30.399 --> 00:11:32.710
the bullies bully you. I was bullied a

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:36.310
lot in school and I had a lot of

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:38.389
learning disabilities,

00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:41.110
and being a child that could barely

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.509
read and do math and do all these

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:46.790
things, I was in special ed all my life.

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:48.870
And being in special ed, every time we

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.030
went to PE or any of those places, I was

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:54.069
brutally picked on every day.

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:02.150
When you get to an adult level,

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:06.230
I realize it is just like at school,

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.990
that you are not a lot of

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:09.509
times invited. You may be a

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:11.110
little different because you had special

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:13.350
needs or whatever.

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:15.350
You can say whatever it is, it is like

00:12:15.350 --> 00:12:15.360
learning

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.509
disabilities or whatever, and you

00:12:17.509 --> 00:12:17.519
are

00:12:17.519 --> 00:12:19.430
still not invited to the cool kid

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:22.949
table, no matter how big the platform

00:12:22.959 --> 00:12:26.629
grows. I ministered to, last week we

00:12:26.639 --> 00:12:27.910
ministered to three and a half million

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:31.190
people just on this alone,

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:32.870
and you think, well, that will get you

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:36.150
into the cool kid table,

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.389
and it

00:12:38.389 --> 00:12:38.399
is

00:12:38.399 --> 00:12:40.629
the offense

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:42.150
and you walk in it, and the Lord said, Brandon, I

00:12:42.150 --> 00:12:42.160
did not

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:43.750
call you to hang around

00:12:43.760 --> 00:12:49.269
them. I need you to be you.

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:51.590
I need you to be you. And in doing so,

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:54.150
it will prove to be accurate. There

00:12:54.150 --> 00:12:54.160
will

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:57.430
be things that you say

00:12:57.440 --> 00:13:00.230
that I will tell you to say and it

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.910
will help people and it will change the

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:03.509
nations.

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:07.509
But it will take dying to self.

00:13:07.519 --> 00:13:09.350
And the more you squirm, the more you

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:12.150
realize you are not dead.

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:15.110
The more you are offended, it hurts. The

